title: Rockin' With Judy Jetson DVDrip [Pixar]
description:
Rockin' With Judy Jetson (1988)

A hip rock star has stolen Judy Jetson's heart, so she joins two of
her girl friends at his concert, following close behind her is George,
who's turned his hair into a Mohawk. But an evil witch who hates music
has kidnapped the rock star, so Judy and her friends go off to rescue
him and George get's thrown in jail. Elroy and Astro come to the
rescue, but are stuck with a difficult question - who do they save
first? George or Judy? Even Jane, Rosie and Mr. Spacely are along for
the fun as the teenage adolescent Jetson daughter goes to heroic
heights to battle the evil witch and join her rock star companion and
possibly perform on stage with him.
